metadata.description:
Happy Holidays & all that Jazz.

Backstory:
Created & Released on December 23rd, 2010.
Produced by Dutchyyy


The title of this track comes from the blog I used to run. "The Hobbyshop Hero" Originally Launched in 2006, I think my last post was 2011. Focused on highlighting music, toys, videogames, streetwear, collectables...  You know, Nerd Stuff. 

https://thehobbyshophero.blogspot.com 

I definitely miss the blog era.  As a creative and A collector, it was a dope way to share inspiration. While my blog might be super dated, and this song is super dated, The sentiment of being grateful & the spirit of collecting and sharing inspiration is eternal.  I thought it was a good day to solidify a little ghost of Xmas past on blockchain to live forever. 

Love, Light & All that Jazz.

Sincerely, Dutch 
12.25.22
